data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT for this 4 bedroom with BONUS home! This is all the space you will ever need! Come check out this gorgeous Brewster floor plan, located in a highly sought after neighborhood! This is central to all things Clarksville, close to the interstate, close to 101st/warfield, close to exit 4 with all the restaurants and malls, and highly-rated schools. Curb appeal is present with a front porch with space, walk into high ceilings and beautiful fireplace. The kitchen has tons of cabinets space, granite countertops, and the sink facing the living room. Back yard is fenced and accompanied with a covered back deck. Primary bedroom on the main floor, along with laundry room, and half-bath for guests. Upstairs you'll find three other SPACIOUS bedrooms, and a bonus room! This luxury home is here for you and any of your family needs!
